title: Tankstelle an der A5 brennt - Fahrer stirbt | hessenschau
description:

Demnach war das Auto in Brand geraten, als es mit der S√§ule kollidierte. Die Flammen sprangen auf einen Transporter √ºber, der an den Zapfs√§ulen stand, und breiteten sich auch auf dem Dach der Tankstelle aus.

channelDescription:
Dafina Zeqiri's Official YouTube Channel

Dafina Zeqiri was born on 14 April 1989 in an Albanian family in the city of Varberg, Sweden. Her siblings are Tringa and Besa.

Being more than your typical Indie Artist, songwriter & composer with her smooth, electrifying, but bold vocals, she began singing at the age of 10 - where she performed her own songs at a children‚Äôs festival in Sweden. Her talent comes naturally from her mother, Melihate Zeqiri (a former singer of the 1980's). At 17, her career became a priority and within a year she gained popularity in Kosovo after winning multiple awards, making her name holistically known. 

In 2018, she decided to continue her career independently with the support of her team MONEYZ in Kosovo, continuously dropping one hit record after another with amazing music-videos.

In 2021, Dafina is planning on dropping her Album ‚ÄúDafin√´ Moj‚Äù where you will find a couple of features with some of the most popular artists in the Albanian Industry.
